            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Preserve This Paper</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The editor urges readers to keep this issue of the Vindicator because it
                    contains the texts of the Currency, Tax, and Military bills. He warns that they
                    might seem harsh but that everyone has a duty to comply with them in order to
                    move the country to a more pleasant state.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
